show.title: Na Umr Ki Seema Ho
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/qBzSDE
show.description: A wealthy yet lonely ex-army man, Siddharth Kapoor, crosses paths with Sana, a resilient food stall owner grappling with heartbreak, family strife, and a painful past. Brought together by Kapoor’s adopted daughter in a chance matchmaking attempt, their story unfolds into a deep emotional journey. Kapoor conceals his identity to test Sana’s sincerity, but for Sana, this bond transcends romance — ultimately leading her to an unexpected reunion with the daughter she lost five years ago.
